(4. Health and Benefits) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(The company provides medical, dental, and vision insurance to all) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(full-time employees, effective on the first day of employment.) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(A 401\(k\) retirement plan is available with a company match of up to 4%) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(of the employee's annual salary.) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
() Tj
T*
/F2 12 Tf
(5. IT and Data Security) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(Employees must use company-issued devices for all work activities and) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(enable two-factor authentication on all corporate accounts. Confidential) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(data may not be stored on personal devices or shared outside the company) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(without written authorization from the Data Protection Officer.) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
() Tj
T*
/F2 12 Tf
(6. Code of Conduct) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(All employees are expected to treat colleagues, customers, and partners) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(with respect. Harassment or discrimination of any kind is not tolerated) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(and should be reported to Human Resources. Violations of this policy may) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
(result in disciplinary action, up to and including termination.) Tj
T*
/F1 10 Tf
() Tj
